---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<header class="site-header">
		<a class="brand" href="/">sekayu122</a>
		<nav aria-label="Primary navigation">
			<a href="#work">Work</a>
			<a href="#projects">Projects</a>
			<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
		</nav>
	</header>

	<main class="page">
		<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
			<div class="hero-copy">
				<p class="eyebrow">Hardware / 3DCG / Image Processing / Automation</p>
				<h1 id="hero-title">手を動かして、仕組みを形にする。</h1>
				<p class="lead">
					sekayu122 は、電子工作、3DCG、画像処理、mac mini
					自動化を中心に、実験と制作の記録を積み上げている個人ポートフォリオです。
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions">
					<a class="primary-link" href="#projects">制作を見る</a>
					<a class="text-link" href="#contact">連絡する</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="signal-board" aria-hidden="true">
				<div class="board-top">
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
				</div>
				<div class="trace-grid">
					<span class="trace trace-a"></span>
					<span class="trace trace-b"></span>
					<span class="trace trace-c"></span>
					<span class="chip chip-main"></span>
					<span class="chip chip-sub"></span>
					<span class="node node-a"></span>
					<span class="node node-b"></span>
					<span class="node node-c"></span>
				</div>
				<div class="board-footer">
					<span>GPIO</span>
					<span>CV</span>
					<span>RENDER</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section intro" aria-labelledby="intro-title">
			<div>
				<p class="section-kicker">Profile</p>
				<h2 id="intro-title">小さな検証から、使える道具まで。</h2>
			</div>
			<p>
				物理的なデバイス、画像処理のパイプライン、日常作業を軽くする自動化を横断して制作しています。
				観察、試作、ログ化を大切にし、あとから再現できる形で知見を残します。
			</p>
		</section>

		<section id="work" class="section" aria-labelledby="work-title">
			<div class="section-heading">
				<p class="section-kicker">Focus</p>
				<h2 id="work-title">制作領域</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="focus-grid">
				<article>
					<span class="marker electronics"></span>
					<h3>電子工作</h3>
					<p>センサー、マイコン、入出力回路を組み合わせたプロトタイピング。</p>
				</article>
				<article>
					<span class="marker cg"></span>
					<h3>3DCG</h3>
					<p>形状、質感、レンダリングを通したビジュアル検証と表現。</p>
				</article>
				<article>
					<span class="marker vision"></span>
					<h3>画像処理</h3>
					<p>撮影画像や生成画像を扱う解析、変換、ワークフロー設計。</p>
				</article>
				<article>
					<span class="marker automation"></span>
					<h3>mac mini 自動化</h3>
					<p>常時稼働マシンを使ったタスク実行、監視、制作環境の整備。</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="projects" class="section projects" aria-labelledby="projects-title">
			<div class="section-heading">
				<p class="section-kicker">Selected Projects</p>
				<h2 id="projects-title">最近の制作テーマ</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="project-list">
				<article>
					<div class="project-visual visual-circuit" aria-hidden="true"></div>
					<div>
						<p class="project-type">Prototype</p>
						<h3>センサー入力の実験ログ</h3>
						<p>入力値のゆらぎを観察し、回路とソフトウェアの両側から安定化を試す記録。</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article>
					<div class="project-visual visual-render" aria-hidden="true"></div>
					<div>
						<p class="project-type">Visual Study</p>
						<h3>3DCG と画像処理の連携</h3>
						<p>レンダリング結果を画像処理に渡し、表現や検査に使えるパイプラインを検討。</p>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article>
					<div class="project-visual visual-server" aria-hidden="true"></div>
					<div>
						<p class="project-type">Automation</p>
						<h3>mac mini 運用メモ</h3>
						<p>定期実行、ファイル整理、通知など、制作を支える自動化の設定を整理。</p>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="contact" class="contact" aria-labelledby="contact-title">
			<div>
				<p class="section-kicker">Contact</p>
				<h2 id="contact-title">制作メモと実験記録を更新中。</h2>
			</div>
			<a class="primary-link" href="https://github.com/sekayu122">GitHubを見る</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.site-header {
		position: sticky;
		top: 0;
		z-index: 10;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 1rem clamp(1rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.1);
		background: rgba(247, 246, 241, 0.92);
		backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
	}

	.brand {
		font-weight: 800;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	nav {
		display: flex;
		gap: clamp(0.75rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	nav a,
	.text-link {
		color: #48575b;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	nav a:hover,
	.text-link:hover {
		color: #1d2528;
	}

	.page {
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 0.9fr);
		gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
		align-items: center;
		min-height: calc(100vh - 4rem);
		padding: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
	}

	.hero-copy {
		max-width: 720px;
	}

	.eyebrow,
	.section-kicker,
	.project-type {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		color: #aa3f2e;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1 {
		max-width: 11ch;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.8rem);
		line-height: 0.98;
	}

	h2,
	h3,
	p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
		line-height: 1.08;
	}

	h3 {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}

	.lead {
		max-width: 650px;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		color: #48575b;
		font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.primary-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 44px;
		padding: 0.8rem 1.1rem;
		border: 1px solid #1d2528;
		background: #1d2528;
		color: #fff;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.primary-link:hover {
		background: #314045;
	}

	.signal-board {
		position: relative;
		width: min(100%, 520px);
		aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
		justify-self: center;
		border: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.15);
		background:
			linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28)),
			#d8e4dd;
		box-shadow: 18px 18px 0 #2f6f70;
	}

	.board-top,
	.board-footer {
		position: absolute;
		left: 1.25rem;
		right: 1.25rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
	}

	.board-top {
		top: 1.25rem;
	}

	.board-top span {
		width: 0.7rem;
		height: 0.7rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #1d2528;
	}

	.board-footer {
		bottom: 1.25rem;
		color: #48575b;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
	}

	.trace-grid {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 4rem 2rem;
		background-image:
			linear-gradient(rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
			linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
		background-size: 34px 34px;
	}

	.trace,
	.chip,
	.node {
		position: absolute;
		display: block;
	}

	.trace {
		background: #2f6f70;
	}

	.trace-a {
		top: 18%;
		left: 12%;
		width: 76%;
		height: 6px;
	}

	.trace-b {
		top: 18%;
		left: 58%;
		width: 6px;
		height: 55%;
	}

	.trace-c {
		top: 70%;
		left: 20%;
		width: 42%;
		height: 6px;
		background: #aa3f2e;
	}

	.chip {
		border: 2px solid #1d2528;
		background: #f7f6f1;
	}

	.chip-main {
		top: 34%;
		left: 18%;
		width: 42%;
		aspect-ratio: 1;
	}

	.chip-sub {
		top: 50%;
		right: 10%;
		width: 24%;
		aspect-ratio: 1.35;
		background: #f2c14e;
	}

	.node {
		width: 18px;
		height: 18px;
		border: 3px solid #1d2528;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #f7f6f1;
	}

	.node-a {
		top: 14%;
		left: 9%;
	}

	.node-b {
		top: 67%;
		left: 17%;
	}

	.node-c {
		top: 70%;
		left: 57%;
	}

	.section {
		padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
	}

	.intro {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
		gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.1);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.1);
		background: #fffdf8;
	}

	.intro p:last-child {
		color: #48575b;
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.section-heading {
		display: flex;
		align-items: end;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.focus-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.14);
		border-left: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.14);
	}

	.focus-grid article {
		min-height: 250px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-right: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.14);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.14);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
	}

	.focus-grid p,
	.project-list p {
		color: #48575b;
		line-height: 1.65;
	}

	.marker {
		display: block;
		width: 42px;
		height: 42px;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.electronics {
		background: #2f6f70;
	}

	.cg {
		background: #f2c14e;
		clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
	}

	.vision {
		border: 10px solid #aa3f2e;
		border-radius: 999px;
	}

	.automation {
		background:
			linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 42%, #1d2528 42%, #1d2528 58%, transparent 58%),
			linear-gradient(transparent 42%, #1d2528 42%, #1d2528 58%, transparent 58%),
			#d8e4dd;
	}

	.projects {
		background: #1d2528;
		color: #f7f6f1;
	}

	.projects .section-kicker,
	.projects .project-type {
		color: #f2c14e;
	}

	.projects .project-list p {
		color: #d9e1df;
	}

	.project-list {
		display: grid;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.project-list article {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 220px minmax(0, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(247, 246, 241, 0.16);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
	}

	.project-visual {
		min-height: 150px;
		background-color: #d8e4dd;
	}

	.visual-circuit {
		background-image:
			linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0 18%, #2f6f70 18% 22%, transparent 22%),
			linear-gradient(transparent 0 44%, #aa3f2e 44% 49%, transparent 49%),
			radial-gradient(circle at 72% 48%, #1d2528 0 11px, transparent 12px);
	}

	.visual-render {
		background:
			linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 35%, rgba(29, 37, 40, 0.22) 35% 50%, transparent 50%),
			linear-gradient(45deg, #f2c14e 0 45%, #fffdf8 45% 70%, #aa3f2e 70%);
	}

	.visual-server {
		background:
			linear-gradient(#1d2528 0 0) 24px 30px / calc(100% - 48px) 18px no-repeat,
			linear-gradient(#2f6f70 0 0) 24px 72px / calc(100% - 48px) 18px no-repeat,
			linear-gradient(#aa3f2e 0 0) 24px 114px / calc(100% - 48px) 18px no-repeat,
			#d8e4dd;
	}

	.contact {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		background: #fffdf8;
	}

	.contact h2 {
		max-width: 760px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.hero,
		.intro,
		.project-list article {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.signal-board {
			justify-self: start;
			max-width: 440px;
		}

		.focus-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.site-header {
			align-items: flex-start;
			flex-direction: column;
		}

		.hero {
			min-height: auto;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 16vw, 4.8rem);
		}

		.signal-board {
			box-shadow: 10px 10px 0 #2f6f70;
		}

		.focus-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.focus-grid article {
			min-height: 210px;
		}

		.contact {
			align-items: flex-start;
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
